{"id":267429,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/12/维权网-上海维权人士冯正虎连续三天遭到警方传/","date":"2012-12-09T23:46:59Z","modified":"2012-12-09T23:46:59Z","title":"维权网 | 上海维权人士冯正虎连续三天遭到警方传唤（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-DjYx6ddbDHM/UMStxUhqQ4I/AAAAAAAAVnY/gkuQ3CxO92Q/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE0qqq.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-DjYx6ddbDHM/UMStxUhqQ4I/AAAAAAAAVnY/gkuQ3CxO92Q/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE0qqq.jpg\" />  </a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员亦然报道）上海维权人士冯正虎连续三天以来，都受到辖区五角场派出所的传唤，每天上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>点左右一直到晚上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>点以后，被传唤十余个小时，以此变相限制冯正虎人身自由。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据 冯正虎 先生说，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>日</span><span>警察出具的仍是刑事传唤证，被传唤的时候，由于身体不适，他只能带被子到派出所，一上午躺在派出所的长椅上，也无警察问话。直到下午警察随便问了在哪个大学毕业等与传唤无关的话后离开，晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">40</span><span>分冯正虎才获释回家。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>由于冯正虎自</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日</span><span>开始被囚禁在家中无法出门长达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">268</span><span>天，期间腿部受伤，现在仍隐隐作痛，已经与医院预约好</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日下午</span><span>到医院检查，由于已经连续被传唤三天，明天还不知能否正常去医院。今年六四期间，冯正虎虽然被囚禁在家，但仍受到警方连续五天的传唤。一样是每天早上被警察带走，晚上再被送回家。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>冯正虎</span><span>先生表示，在中国真正实现民主宪政的过程中，总会有许许多多的人付出努力和牺牲，他对自己遭受的迫害早已经看开想开了。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>本网相关报道请见：上海维权人士冯正虎被传唤抄家</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://wqw2010.blogspot.jp/2012/12/blog-post_8043.html\">http://wqw2010.blogspot.jp/2012/12/blog-post_8043.html</a></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-6102328957328246854?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}